  5. USER MANAGEMENT — Cognito provides a proper user directory. Passwords
                       can be reset, accounts can be disabled, MFA can be
                       added — all via the AWS Console.

  6. AUDIT TRAIL — DynamoDB and API Gateway both log all activity to
